description:
On today’s show, Emily is joined by entrepreneur, writer, media personality, & founder of The Satisfied Mama’s, Dana B. Myers. They discuss the importance of reclaiming your sexuality and ways to become fully present with your body.

They talk about discovering your mojo – with or without kids in the picture, why mom guilt exists and how to get over it, as well as hacks to keep sex top of mind.
